---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Konjički sport" activePage="/konjicki-sport">

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <div class="page-hero-breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Naslovnica</a>
        <span class="sep">›</span>
        <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Konjički sport</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Konjički sport</h1>
      <p>Tri FEI discipline u kojima muškarci i žene ravnopravno nastupaju — individualno ili timski. Od olimpijskih prepona do elegancije dresure i izdržljivosti daljinskog jahanja.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PREPONSKO JAHANJE -->
  <section class="section" id="preponsko">
    <div class="discipline-block reveal">
      <div class="discipline-img">
        <img src="/images/uploads/preponsko.jpg" alt="Preponsko jahanje">
        <span class="discipline-img-badge">Olimpijska disciplina</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discipline-text">
        <div class="discipline-number">01</div>
        <h2>Preponsko jahanje</h2>
        <p>Preponsko jahanje je bez sumnje najpoznatija disciplina konjičkog sporta prepoznata od strane FEI. Muškarci i žene ravnopravno se natječu, individualno ili timski, a disciplina je jedna od tri natjecateljske na Olimpijskim igrama.</p>
        <p>Skakanje konjima počelo se razvijati u 18. stoljeću, kad je lov na lisice zahtijevao preskakanje ograda. Prvo dokumentirano natjecanje organizirano je 1866. u Parizu, a olimpijskom disciplinom postalo je 1912. godine u Stockholmu.</p>
        <div class="discipline-features">
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Brzina</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Preciznost</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Spretnost</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Olimpijske igre od 1912.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- DRESURNO JAHANJE -->
  <section class="section" id="dresurno">
    <div class="discipline-block reverse reveal">
      <div class="discipline-img">
        <img src="/images/uploads/dresurno.jpg" alt="Dresurno jahanje">
        <span class="discipline-img-badge">Temeljna disciplina</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discipline-text">
        <div class="discipline-number">02</div>
        <h2>Dresurno jahanje</h2>
        <p>Dresurno jahanje je temeljna disciplina konjičkog sporta u kojoj se isprepliće sport i umjetnost suradnje jahača i konja. Cilj je izvesti testove koji u sebi sadrže razne načine kretanja konja — od hoda u kas, zaustavljanja na određenim pozicijama, uz poštivanje obrazaca kretnji i figura.</p>
        <p>Jahač i konj u suradnji izvode unaprijed definirane testove koje moraju znati napamet. Posebnost su "Freestyle" testovi u kojima jahač definira vlastitu koreografiju uz glazbu. U posljednjih nekoliko godina dresurno jahanje privlači sve veći broj mladih natjecatelja.</p>
        <div class="discipline-features">
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Elegancija</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Sklad</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Tehnička izvedba</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Freestyle uz glazbu</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- DALJINSKO JAHANJE -->
  <section class="section" id="daljinsko">
    <div class="discipline-block reveal">
      <div class="discipline-img">
        <img src="/images/uploads/daljinsko.jpg" alt="Daljinsko jahanje">
        <span class="discipline-img-badge">Najbrže rastuća disciplina</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discipline-text">
        <div class="discipline-number">03</div>
        <h2>Daljinsko jahanje</h2>
        <p>Daljinsko jahanje (endurance) je natjecanje kojim se provjerava brzina i izdržljivost konja, te jahačevo dobro poznavanje konja i terena. Iako se jahačima mjeri vrijeme, naglasak je na okončanju natjecanja u dobroj fizičkoj kondiciji konja.</p>
        <p>Postavši FEI disciplina 1982. godine, endurance je danas najbrže rastuća konjička disciplina. Natjecanja se sastoje od određenog broja faza, s obaveznim veterinarskim pregledima na svakih 40 km. Jahači imaju slobodu odabrati tempo od starta do cilja.</p>
        <div class="discipline-features">
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Izdržljivost</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Strategija</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Dobrobit konja</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>FEI disciplina od 1982.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OLYMPIC FACTS -->
  <section class="olympic-bar">
    <div class="olympic-inner reveal">
      <div class="olympic-item">
        <div class="olympic-icon"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="olympic-value">1912.</div>
        <div class="olympic-label">Konjički sport na Olimpijskim igrama</div>
      </div>
      <div class="olympic-item">
        <div class="olympic-icon"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="olympic-value">3</div>
        <div class="olympic-label">Olimpijske discipline konjičkog sporta</div>
      </div>
      <div class="olympic-item">
        <div class="olympic-icon"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="olympic-value">Jednako</div>
        <div class="olympic-label">Muškarci i žene natječu se ravnopravno</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLUBS CTA -->
  <section class="clubs-cta">
    <div class="clubs-cta-inner reveal">
      <h2>Želiš se baviti konjičkim sportom?</h2>
      <p>Zagrebački konjički savez okuplja kvalitetne škole jahanja i klubove za sve uzraste. Pronađi svoju školu i započni svoju konjičku avanturu.</p>
      <a href="/skole-jahanja" class="btn btn-blue">Pronađi školu jahanja</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .discipline-block { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .discipline-block.reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .discipline-block.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
  .discipline-img { border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/3; position: relative; }
  .discipline-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.6s; }
  .discipline-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .discipline-img-badge { position: absolute; top: 1rem; left: 1rem; background: var(--blue); color: #fff; padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .discipline-block.reverse .discipline-img-badge { left: auto; right: 1rem; }
  .discipline-number { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-pale); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .discipline-text h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .discipline-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .discipline-features { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .discipline-feature { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; background: var(--blue-pale); color: var(--blue); padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .discipline-feature svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .olympic-bar { background: var(--blue); padding: 3.5rem 2rem; }
  .olympic-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .olympic-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 0.8rem; }
  .olympic-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; color: #fff; }
  .olympic-value { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .olympic-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

  .clubs-cta { background: var(--off-white); padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .clubs-cta-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .clubs-cta h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .clubs-cta p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .discipline-block, .discipline-block.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; direction: ltr; }
    .olympic-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
